How to create DSL

Using "DSLConfigDSL"

This specific DSL allows to create new DSL from a library of parameterized nodes, links and groups. The creation process consist in the following steps:

  1. Creating a new workplace at the current level with the name of the new DSL 
  2. Entering this workspace
  3. Opening "Show DSL List" in the popup menu "Tools..."
  4. Select the DSL : "DSLConfigDSL" 
  5. Click on the button "Set DSL for current graph"
  6. Use the elements in the palette to drag and drop nodes, links and groups, menus and link rules.

Using "DesignDSL"

This specific DSL will allow to draw step by step new DSL. The "DesignDSL" is not yet available in MetaFlow 1.0
